name: "Vengance"
description:
"Now I know I´m one step closer... I found what you let me in the road... you son of a gun, I feel in your eyes all that old stories that I know makes you tired... don´t you cry, because is time to fight... let´s burn down again the entire city..."

this is the 7th and final video of a series of visual stories involving the "girl in the red dress" and myself, Lautaro Quiroga, as a character of this metaverse.

girl in the red dress: Camila Pláate.
